<!-- about -->
<section class="buddy-about">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div>
        <h3>BuddyBuddyを使う理由</h3>
        <hr>
          <p>
            Let's imagine that young family has just moved to a new district and they don't know anybody here. They need time to get familiar with neighbors, and they need to understand whether they can entrust to these neighbors. So what should parents do when they have no one to leave children with? That is where "BuddyBuddy" comes to rescue.
          </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- service -->
<section class="buddy-service">
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class>
        <h3>使い方</h3>
        <hr>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="row">
      <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6">
        <div>
          <i class="fas fa-4x fa-search"></i>
          <h2>Discover</h2>
          <p>Search buddies by profile, location, and category.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6">
        <div>
          <i class="fas fa-4x fa-comments"></i>
          <h2>Request</h2>
          <p>Chat with your buddy and ask a request!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6">
        <div>
          <i class="fas fa-4x fa-calendar-alt"></i>
          <h2>Book</h2>
          <p>Find times that work best and book instantly.</p>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="col-lg-3 col-md-6">
        <div>
          <i class="fas fa-4x fa-heart"></i>
          <h2>Experience</h2>
          <p>Show your Buddy confirmation, learn and play with your best buddy!</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>



